[[Newcastle]] in [[United Kingdom|Britain]] is a coal mining, distributing and selling hub. Hence the phrase "carry coal to Newcastle" or "Sell coal in Newcastle" is used to describe a foolhardy or pointless action.

==People who have tried==

[[Timothy Dexter]], an [[United States of America|American]] buissinessman did export coal to newcastle, which happened to arrive during a miners strike and thus made a killing for him.

